\p{The excursion of the meeting included several stops, including two interesting Viana museums, an archaelogical site on the nearby mountaintop, and a memorable trip to Camarido Beach, at the northernmost tip of Portugal, with Spanish Galicia just to the north along the road from Portugal to Santiago de Compostela.}
