\p{After the meeting had formally concluded, [[okmij]], [[henglein]], [[matija]], [[tsewell]], [[xnning]] and I climbed to Santuario de Santa Luzia. We took the arduous stairs rather than the funicular, as Matija's wife had forbidden him from Portuguese funiculars after the recent [Ascensor da Glória derailment](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ascensor_da_Glória_derailment), which led to me overdoing it and nearly fainting, but in recompense Matija bought me a beer at the top of the mountain which made it (mostly) worth it! }
\p{Hopefully I can make it to the next meeting in Estonia next year!}
